# CODEOWNERS for sunflower-land-overview
#
# Auto-requests review on every PR. Syntax is gitignore-style, with one
# important difference: the *last* matching pattern wins. So put the
# broad default first and specific overrides below it.
#
# When a co-maintainer joins, override specific paths below the default.
# Suggested patterns to add at that point:
#
#   /.github/                — CI workflows and protection rulesets
#   /src/api/                — Cloudflare Worker (handles MASTER_SECRET)
#   /src/sw.ts               — service worker (push notifications)
#   /src/notifications/      — push subscription handling
#   /src/game/ /src/timers/  — upstream-game bridge (see CONTRIBUTING.md
#                              "Never replicate functions from the submodule")
#   /wrangler.jsonc /vite.worker.config.ts — Worker build/runtime config
#   /LICENSE /SECURITY.md /CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md /CONTRIBUTING.md
#                            — governance; keep owner approval explicit
#
# Until then, one owner is enough.

